title: Remote Viewing Interviews - Three Sessions
description:
Ever since the US government officially closed the doors
of their Remote Viewing & Remote Influencing programs several of the
original subjects & agents who were recruited have founded 
RV schools of their own. 

The U.S.A. is not the only nation to have created such systems 
of study:

1) What caused all of them to be so enthusiastic about 
the results of their Remote Viewing projects? 

2) what about it eventually made the-powers-that-be so nervous that they decided 
to officially end their research? 

3) Did they really end **all** research?

4) Have all the of the resulting outcomes been revealed in radio or tv interviews 
since - or reported to the public in their entirety? 

Do you have an interest in developing your intuition in ways that can be practically applied in everyday life - whether for fantastically awesome or simple things? 

Three interviews are included in this file - the information here will be very interesting and revealing to anyone who is looking for more in the areas of:

tuning into and/or creating the reality or world you prefer, the law of attraction, psychic development, the Kybalion, universal laws, timelines, the purpose of the space-time "continuum", etc....Enjoy!...and not at all a requirement BUT if you're a sci-fi buff get ready because Trekkies, Battlestar Galactica & Stargate/Atlantis fans will get a kick out of this, too....why you like those shows might make a lot more sense after listening to these audios.
